{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is the Demo version of <strong>FEAR OF FAITH</strong>, a 1-4 <strong>player co-op horror</strong> set in a <i>dieselpunk</i> <i>World War II</i> dark bunkers. You have one day to gather resources, manage your rising <strong>FEAR</strong>, and pay the <strong>TITHE</strong> before darkness overtakes you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The demo showcases the game\u2019s core mechanics, including <i>tactile</i> and <i>physics-based</i> interactions with the world, team-based survival that depends on the crucial role of <strong>generator</strong> maintenance to keep the <strong>lights</strong> on, unique monster behavior, and of course, <strong>FEAR &amp; BEER</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The full game will include multiple days, maps, and cycles, introducing deeper challenges, expanded horrors, and a rich story that unravels the dark lore of this Eternal War.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442790/extras/title-01.png?t=1740598978\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into an alternate <i>World War II era setting</i>, where <strong>dieselpunk</strong> technology and eldritch horrors collide.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Powered by Unreal Engine 5</strong> and latest technologies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442790/extras/room_framed_opt.gif?t=1740598978\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442790/extras/title-02.png?t=1740598978\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you see monsters, corpses, or are covered in darkness - your <strong>FEAR</strong> increases, and if you do not take care of it - soon you will become a <strong>GHOUL</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reduce your <strong>FEAR</strong> with alcohol, keep generator lights on, and take care of your teammates with a good punch of the holy book.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442790/extras/beer_and_ghoul_framed_opt__beer_cutted_.gif?t=1740598978\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442790/extras/title-03.png?t=1740598978\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Like in <i>Amnesia </i>games, you can smoothly interact with doors / chests / traps. But if you have no time - <strong>DON'T HESITATE</strong> - kick it to open faster, but making more noise.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Besides taking items into your inventory, you can grab them and throw anywhere to see what happens. <i>Also your teammates can catch them in fly.</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And what about an oil barrel and a flare? \ud83e\udd14</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442790/extras/bottle_drop_framed_opt.gif?t=1740598978\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3442790/extras/title-04.png?t=1740598978\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Someone </i></strong>from your crew must become a<strong> LIGHT KEEPER</strong> and stay on the surface to refuel the bunker generator and keep an eye on the radar to notify you about any threats or valua